f'(z).
\begin{align}f'(z) &= (z+2)^2+2(z-1)(z+2)\\ &= \bigl((z+2)+2(z-1)\bigr)(z+2)\\ &= (z+2+2z-2)(z+2)\\ &= 3z(z+2).\end{align}
